    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html><html style=\"font-size: 85px;\"><head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1\">\n    <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n    <meta name=\"renderer\" content=\"webkit\">\n    <title>清华大学建筑学院</title>\n    <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"清华大学建筑学院,建筑学院,世界一流,建筑学,中国特色，城市规划，建筑系\">\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"清华大学是中国著名高等学府，是中国高层次人才培养和科学技术研究的重要基地。清华大学的前身是清华学堂，成立于1911年。截至2017年，清华大学设有20个学院、58个系，已成为一所具有理学、工学、文学、艺术学、历史学、哲学、经济学、管理学、法学、教育学和医学等学科门类的综合性、研究型、开放式大学。截至2017年8月31号，清华大学在学学生总数为47762人，其中本科生15619人、硕士生19062人、博士生13081人。\">\n   \n    <link href=\"/sites/css/font.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link href=\"/sites/css/index.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link href=\"/sites/css/phone.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/sites/js/swiper/swiper-3.4.2.min.css\">\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/jquery-3.3.1.min.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/js.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/swiper/swiper-3.4.2.jquery.min.js\"></script>\n</head>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<body>\n<div class=\"headD\"></div>\n   \n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"head\">\n    <div class=\"wal\">\n        <a href=\"\" class=\"logo\"></a>\n        <a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"navA\"></a>\n        <dl class=\"btn\">\n            <dd><a href=\"/column/INDEX\" class=\"on\">CN</a></dd>\n            <dd><a href=\"/column/Home\">EN</a></dd>\n            \n            \n \n            \n            \n            <dd class=\"search\" value=\"搜索\"> \n              <form name=\"form1\" id=\"search-form-header\" action=\"/column/search\" target=\"_blank\" method=\"post\">\n                   <div class=\"input\">    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"curpage\" value=\"1\">\n\t               <input name=\"key\" type=\"text\" class=\"inp\" value=\"\" onfocus=\"this.value=''\" onblur=\"if(this.value==''){this.value='';}\">\n                </div>  \n\t         </form>\n        \n           </dd>  \n            <div class=\"submit\">      \n                 <a id=\"searchbtn\" href=\"javascript:;\" onclick=\"$('#search-form-header').submit();\" class=\"btn\" title=\"搜索\">搜索</a>\n           </div> \n      \n            \n        </dl>\n        <div class=\"nav\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/INDEX\">首页</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jj\">简介</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/dt\">动态</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/xs\">系所</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/zs\">招生</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jx\">教学</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/ky\">科研</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/rw\">人物</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jl\">交流</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/lj\">链接</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"characterShow_01\">\n    <div class=\"wal\">\n         <div class=\"info\"><a href=\"/column/INDEX\">首页</a><a href=\"/column/rw\"><b>·</b>人物</a>  <a href=\"/column/sz\"><b>·</b>师资</a>  <a href=\"/column/rw_jzx\"><b>·</b>建筑系</a>  </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"name\">李晓东</div>\n        <div class=\"msg\">\n            电话：86-10-62794237 <br>\n            传真：86-10-62770314 <br>\n            E-mail：\n        </div>\n    \n       <div class=\"img\"><img src=\"/upload_files/image/1572130143325_1C.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n   \n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"wal characterShow\">\n   \n     <div class=\"content\"><p style=\"text-indent: 32px;line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">李晓东&nbsp; &nbsp;博士生导师</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">主持李晓东工作室 Li Xiaodong Atelier</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">教育背景</span></strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">：</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">1991 - 1993：</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">建筑学博士，荷兰德尔富特大学及安德毫芬大学建筑系，荷兰</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">1989 - 1991：</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">城市设计硕士，荷兰德尔富特大学及安德毫芬大学建筑系，荷兰</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">1979 - 1984：</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">建筑学学士，清华大学建筑系</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\"><br></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">工作简历</span></strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">：</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">1997 - 2001:</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Professor, history and theory, School of Architecture,&nbsp; Tsinghua University, 教授, 清华大学建筑学院</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Chair, Department of Architecture, Tsinghua University, 主任，清华大学，建筑系</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Director, EMPA (English Master Program of Architecture), School of Architecture, Tsinghua University, 清华大学建筑学院，国际部主任</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Atelier Li Xiaodong, Singapore 李晓东工作室，新加坡</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Associate Professor School of Architecture, Faculty of Architecture, Building &amp; Real Estate, The National University of Singapore (NUS),&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">副教授，新加坡国立大学建筑系</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Assistant Professor, School of Architecture, Faculty of Architecture, Building &amp; Real Estate, The National University of Singapore (NUS), Singapore, 助理教授，新加坡国立大学建筑系</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">1995 - 1997:</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Architect and partner, Leex Architecture and Urban Development, Delft, Netherlands</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">建筑师及合伙人， 莱克斯建筑与城市设计，荷兰</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">1993 - 1995:</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Design Architect, de Architeckten Cie，Amsterdam, Netherlands</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">设计师，斯建筑设计事务所，荷兰</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">1989 - 1993:</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Research Fellow, School of Architecture, Eindhoven University of Technology and Delft University of Technology, Netherlands</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">研究员，荷兰德尔富特大学及安德毫芬大学建筑系，荷兰</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">1984 - 1989:</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Lecturer, School&nbsp; of Architecture, Tsinghua University</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">助教，清华大学建筑系</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">主要学术成果</span></strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">：</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2018， WAF(世界建筑节)终审评委（super judge),Amsterdam</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2014， winner, Moriyama RAIC International Prize of Architecture</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2013, “建筑的必要性国际宣言”国际可持续社区建筑评选第一名, (Architecture of Necessity) winner,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">(Sweden)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2013， AD 中国最具影响力100位建筑，设计精英</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2012，世界建筑节，年度世界文化建筑大奖， WAF(World Architecture Festival)，winner (cultural category),&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">(Singapore)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2012, 世界年度八大绿色建筑，英国泰晤士报（Times）</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2012, 美国·建筑师协会荣誉院士， Hon. FAIA （US）</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2011，筑龙网中国建筑十年，最受关注奖</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2011, GQ 年度人物(最佳设计师),(GQ men of the Year)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2010 ，“阿卡罕”建筑奖（Aga Khan Award for Architecture， winner）</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2010 ，优胜奖， 《世界建筑》 中国建筑奖， （winner，World Architecture）</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2009，英国“建筑回顾” 世界新锐建筑奖 第一名， (AR emerging architecture awards winner)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2005-06，年度亚洲建筑金奖（ARCASIA Gold Medal）</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2005，联合国教科文文化保护创新奖(UESCO Jury Award for Innovation)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2004，美国环境设计与研究协会年度最佳设计奖(Best Design Award, EDRA (Environment Design and</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Research Association) Places annual awards, USA.)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2005，英国“建筑回顾”世界新锐建筑奖二等奖(AR+D Highly Recommended)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2006，美国“建筑实录”中国建筑奖最佳公共建筑奖（Architectural Records business week&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">China Awards, best public Building）</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">&nbsp;(2000)英国皇家建筑师协会主席奖, 优秀教师奖.(RIBA(Royal Institute of British Architects)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Tutor Prize, The President's medals)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2001，美国注册建筑师协会教师奖(Society of American Registered Architects, Tutor Prize)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">荷兰德尔富特住宅设计获1996年度荷兰国家优秀设计奖 (1994-1996)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">荷兰阿姆斯特丹瑞士保险公司总部获国家竞赛一等奖(1993-1995)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">发表学术专著 3本，学术论文近三十篇, 其中五篇发表在国际一流期刊上。</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\"><br></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">作品</span></strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">：</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2011：&nbsp; Liyuan Library, 篱苑书屋</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2010-：&nbsp; Meditation space， Beijing （on-going）</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2009-:&nbsp; &nbsp;School of Architecture expansion project (Tsinghua University. Beijing)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2008-：&nbsp; Artist clubhouse， （Hangzhou）</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2008-09：Bridge School （Fujian）</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2009-：&nbsp; Master Plan for Juyuan （sichuan）</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2006:&nbsp; &nbsp; Pheonix TV Media Center (Beijing)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2005-09：Waterhouse （YunNan）</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2004:&nbsp; &nbsp; Zen Hotel (HeNan)</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2003-04：Yuhu Primary School （YunNan）</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2003:&nbsp; &nbsp; Entrance for Zoology Singapore (Singapore)</span></p> </div>\n</div>\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"footFollow\">\n    <div class=\"title\">——<em>关注我们</em>——</div>\n    <ul>\n        <li><a href=\"javascript:;\"><img src=\"/sites/image/nimg42_1.png\" alt=\"\"></a>\n            <div class=\"layer\"><img src=\"/sites/image/img198.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n        </li>\n        <li><a href=\"\"><img src=\"/sites/image/nimg42_2.png\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"foot\">\n    <div class=\"wal\">\n        <div class=\"logo\">\n            <div><a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/thu2018/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"/sites/image/img40_1.png\" alt=\"\"></a></div>\n            <div><a href=\"